This paper is primarily focused on image generation using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) also suggests that it could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the structure of images, which could potentially fall under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
